data.description:
Stunning home built by Grand Homes in 2013 (Hamptons Floor Plan). Spacious home situated on almost half of an acre lot is just steps away from the water’s edge of Lake Lewisville, with access to walking trails on the Lake Side. Located in the The Tribute Lakeside Golf & Resort Community in the heart of North Dallas. Plenty of Amenities including a Kayak ramp to access the lake, Pickle Ball Court, walking and bike trails and multiple pools. This home boasts all new recently upgraded luxury bathroom tiles and shower glasses, double staircases with beautiful chandeliers, a family room with high Cathedral style ceiling and wooden beams, a chef’s gourmet kitchen and a larger master bedroom and all bathrooms beautifully upgraded. Open concept design with 6 bedrooms, 5 and a half baths make this an ideal home for you to entertain your guests.
Side access driveway to the 2 car garage plus a golf cart garage for golf lovers. The huge backyard could be for a Texas size pool if desired!!
